    "title": "Normalization and denormalization",
    "type": "text",
    "completed": false,
    "text": "<p>In this section you learn about normalization and denormalization.</p>\r\n<p>Normalization and denormalization are two techniques to transform data in order to create a model that is easier to query and navigate.</p>\r\n<p>This section is required before moving forward with the following sections.</p>",
