    "title": "Star schemas",
    "type": "text",
    "completed": false,
    "text": "<p style=\"color: #333333;\">In this section, we introduce the concept of a star schema and how important it is in the design of any analytical data model.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #333333;\">This section is important to understand the more common and efficient data modeling pattern that can be used in any product, not only in Power BI.</p>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>",
