    "title": "Data modeling scenarios",
    "type": "text",
    "completed": false,
    "text": "<p>The following examples introduce the right approach to transform a data source in a model that follows the rules of star schemas.</p>\r\n<p>You will also see some example of common data modeling scenario.</p>\r\n<p>A deeper explanation of each example and a larger number of scenarios are included in the complete course <a href=\"/p/data-modeling-for-power-bi-video-course/\">Data Modeling for Power BI</a>.</p>",
